          "id": "756aa496a88e3bce522738eb2b466e6147542aef",
          "message": "chore(misc/genproto): add comment to generated go files (#5264)\n\nPutting this line at the top of the files generated by genproto makes\nthem invisible to linters and other go tooling.\n\nCurrently, if you run `make lint` on a working directory with pbbindings\nfiles, you get 1k+ linting issues relating to those files. With this PR,\nthose are no longer analyzed.",
          "timestamp": "2026-03-23T13:49:11+01:00",
          "tree_id": "c9dce9d6def8d026d537603670f3af0282fc4b94",
